“Na7 bo5, an2-ne--lah, khoaN3 li2 au7 le2-pai3 toh 1-kang u7-eng5, goa2 kap li2 tau3-tin7 khi3.”
“Li2 m7-si7 bin5-a2-chai3 to7 beh tng2-khi3 Hoa-lian5--a? Beh an2-choaN2 poe5 goa2 khi3?”
“Hoa-lian5 hia bo5 siaN2-mih iau3-kin2 e5 tai7-chi3, e7-sai2 khah ban7 tng2--khi3-e5, goa2 chit-ma2 to7 kan-taN chhong3 lun7-bun5 nia5.”
