KhoaN3 A-eng tih khau3, i ka7 A-eng e5 thau5 phou5--khi2-lai5, kim-kim-a2 siong3 A-eng e5 bak8-chiu, khin-siaN-se3-soeh kong2 “Goa2 ai3--li2!” I te7-1-paiN3 tui3 A-eng kong2 “Goa2 ai3--li2!”, te7-1-paiN3 tui3 A-eng piau2-tat sim-i3, siau3-lian5 si5-tai7 sio i3-ai3 e5 phoaN7, keng3-jian5 keng-koe3 kui2-a2-ni5 chiah ka7 ka-ti7 e5 kam2-cheng5 kong2--chhut-lai5.
Khi3 peN7-iN7 kiam2-cha e5 koe3-tng2-kang, A-eng khi3 in chhu3 chhoe7--i, soah khoaN3-tioh8 in tau chin che7 lang5, chiok lau7-jiat8--e5, na2 tih pan7 hi2-su7--leh. In tau thian--nih u7 chiaN5 10-thiah hi2-piaN2, toh-teng2 koh u7 kui2-a2-chiong2 thiap-a2, kho2-leng5 si7 beh soan2 khoaN3 khah sun7-gan2--e5.
