A-eng thiaN kau3 chia, chin3-cheng5 e5 siuN7-hoat koh khah kian-teng7, bak8-chiu kim-kim ka7 siong3, mng7 i kong2 “Li2 kam2 beh toe3 goa2 khi3 Hoa-lian5? Goa2 koh chhun poaN3-ni5 to7 chhut-giap8--a, kau3-si5 lan2 chiah khoaN3 beh koe3 siaN2-mih-khoan2 seng-oah8!”
I ka7 A-eng lam2--leh, kong2 “Ho2! Lan2 cho3-hoe2 khi3 Hoa-lian5 chau2-chhoe7 lan2 e5 bi7-lai5!”
Koe3 tng2-kang, i chhu2-siau kap cha-bou2 lau7-su e5 hun-iok, pou2-sang3 le2-mih8 khi3 tui3-hong chhu3--nih hoe7-sit-le2. A-eng ham7 i kap chhu3--nih chhiau5 be7 ho2-se3, 2-peng5 si7-toa7-lang5 long2 chin be7-tang3 liong7-kai2.
